@271 = ~Fire Trap~
@272 = ~Fire Trap (Invocation/Evocation)
Level: 7
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: special
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: 10-meters radius
Saving Throw: 1/2

This spell will place a Fire Trap at the targeted place. After casting the spell, an orb of fire appears there where the preacher wants. It is visible only to him, and neither detection nor divination allow to reveal to another one. The orb remains there until an imprudent approaches it. At that moment in explodes into a FireBall that inflicts 1D6 damage points per experience level of the spellcaster (maximum 20D6) (a successful saving throw vs. spells allows to halve the received damage).~
