@273 = ~Fire Storm~
@274 = ~Fire Storm (Evocation)
Level: 7
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 30 meters
Duration: 4 rounds
Casting Time: 1 round
Area of Effect: 7-meters radius
Saving Throw: none

When a fire storm spell is cast, the whole area is shot through with sheets of roaring flame and then pelted with fiery balls of lava. Creatures within the area of fire receive 2d8 points of damage plus 1 per level of the priest (or 2D8 +1/level). This assault will last for four rounds and will continue to do damage to the creature during that time unless he moves out of the area of effect. There is no saving throw versus this spell.~
